      "result": "All files written. Here's a complete summary of every change made for alpha-v0.0.3:\n\n---\n\n## Files Created / Updated\n\n### ✳️ New: `scripts/lesson_manager.gd`\nMissing orchestrator script — new file. Connects to all three task `task_completed` signals, tracks progress, shows Dutch \"Taken: N / 3\" label, and navigates back to `main_menu.tscn` after a 2-second celebration pause once both positional tasks + count challenge are done.\n\n### ✏️ Updated: `scripts/red_block.gd`\nAdded `signal task_completed(task_name: String)` and `task_completed.emit(\"red_block\")` call on successful touch. Existing `_touched` guard, `ColorRect`/`Label` animation, and `AudioManager.play_sfx(\"finish\")` all preserved.\n\n### ✏️ Updated: `scripts/blue_target.gd`\nAdded `signal task_completed(task_name: String)` and `task_completed.emit(\"blue_target\")` on discovery. Existing camo colour, brightening animation, and `AudioManager.play_sfx(\"collect\")` preserved.\n\n### ✏️ Updated: `scripts/count_challenge.gd`\nRenamed signal from `challenge_complete` → `task_completed` to match the lesson manager's expectations. Added `AudioManager.play_sfx(\"finish\")` on completion. Uses the existing `count_collectibles` group wiring (Stars 1–3 in the scene).\n\n### ✏️ Updated: `scenes/lesson_1.tscn`\nAdded the missing `LessonManager` script to the root `Lesson1` Node2D, added the `camiel.tscn` instance (was missing), added `ProgressLabel`, updated ext_resource list to 6 entries. Removed spurious `_on_lesson_finished` connection (target method didn't exist).\n\n### ✏️ Updated: `scripts/main_menu.gd`\nAdded `@onready var lesson_button` and `_on_lesson_button_pressed()` → `lesson_1.tscn`. Bumped `version_label` to `alpha-v0.0.3`.\n\n### ✏️ Updated: `scenes/main_menu.tscn`\nAdded `LessonButton` (\"Les\") node to `VBox` between `StartButton` and `VersionLabel`. Wired `pressed` → `_on_lesson_button_pressed`. Bumped version label text to `alpha-v0.0.3`.\n\n### ✏️ Updated: `project.godot`\nBumped `config/name` from `Camiel alpha-v0.0.2` → `Camiel alpha-v0.0.3`.\n\n### ✏️ Updated: `docs/parent-teacher-notes.md`\nFull educator guide: learning objectives for all three micro-tasks, how-to-play walkthrough, classroom setup suggestions, accessibility notes, and technical metadata.\n\n### ✏️ Updated: `docs/accessibility-report.md`\nFull WCAG 2.1 AA audit table: contrast ratios, font sizes, touch targets, motion thresholds, audio/visual redundancy — all ✅ PASS with previous fixes confirmed."
